          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Slider</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is a Part that is:</text></para>
          <list id="8" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">joined to another Part with a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Slide-Joint" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Slide-Joint</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">and its position is specified by a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion-Dimension-FB" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Motion-Dimension FB</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. </text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">It is also a :</text></para>
          <list id="9" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion-Driven-Part" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Motion-Part</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, </text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" style="margin-top:0px;"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Part-Kinematically-Defined" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" translate="true">kinematically-defined Part</link><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" translate="true"> (Solved Part)</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Its motion may be stationary, reciprocating, or sliding with a constant or varying linear velocity.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
